{
  "stem": "11998.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had a very good understanding of what was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we heard rumors-- as that-- people we know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, for example, in 1942, when they were deporting the-- about 1,500 people from Sosnowiec, we saw how they were treated, how they treated the-- the-- the children, how they put them in the-- in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we were-- actually could go and observe them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard that they would just take-- as I didn't see myself, but I heard that somebody saw that they take the babies and they just throw them into the-- the wagons by their feet, as if they were a sack of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew what they were doing with some of the people, you you never-- you always consider yourself, you know, you're strong, and you-- and you're capable of working, and so why would they destroy you?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the destruction for the-- the-- the idea of destruction for-- just for the sake of destruction, I don't think occurred to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it may have occurred to some of my contemporaries, older ones, and certainly my parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we lived a very precarious type of existence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that you had to live a very narrow and-- and-- path, that you could not get a-- into trouble, that the minute you were-- got into trouble, they were jailed, or deported, or, you know, something happened to you.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, that did not stop us from-- kids are kids-- and we-- didn't stop us from going out and having fights with-- with Polish guys and Polish kids that would come and attack us.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
